table-1180-698.caption: The Lord's Prayer
data: Patre nostro, qui es in celos, que tuo nomine fi sanctificato; que tuo regno adveni; que tuo voluntate es facto sicut in celo et in terra. Da hodie ad nos nostro pane quotidiano, et remitte ad nos nostro debitos, sicut et nos remitte ad nostro debitores. Et non induce nos in tentatione, sed libera nos ab malo. Amen.

Patre nostre, qui es in le celos, que tu nomine sia sanctificate; que tu regno veni; que tu voluntate sia facite como in le celo, etiam super le terra. Da nos hodie nostre pan quotidian, e pardona a nos nostre debitas como etiam nos los pardona a nostre debitores. E non induce nos in tentation, sed libera nos del mal. Amen.

Pater noster, qui es in caelis, sanctificetur nomen tuum. Adveniat regnum tuum. Fiat voluntas tua, sicut in caelo, et in terra. Panem nostrum quotidianum da nobis hodie, et dimitte nobis debita nostra, sicut et nos dimittimus debitoribus nostris. Et ne nos inducas in tentationem, sed libera nos a malo. Amen.

Our Father (who are) in heaven, hallowed be your name, your kingdom come, your will be done, on earth as in heaven. Give us today our daily bread. Forgive us our sins as we forgive those who sin against us. Save us from the time of trial and deliver us from evil. Amen.

table-1180-372.caption: References
data: Female lead and prominent protagonist. She is the youngest daughter of Thakur family and youngest daughter-in-law of Prasad family. She was married into the Prasaad family with great difficulty and with great difficulty she has got the Prasaad family to love and accept her. She loves her husband Karan a lot and she is prepared to do anything for him. Abha is the favourite daughter-in-law of the Prasaad family. She and Karan have a daughter named Paavani.
Mother of Jagmohan, she is kind hearted and always shows concern for her children. She always tried to make her son accept Abha as his daughter-in-law. She was murdered by Pratibha's brother Ranjeet.

Head of the Prasaad family, he is very stern on his decisions and expects everyone to heed and follow them. He buys Swarn Bhawan from its auction. He was against Abha & Karan's marriage, but reluctantly accepted it. He hated Abha as she was his biggest enemy's daughter but later, Abha was able to win his and other family members' heart. He died in accident with Vimal, Prakash and Veer.
Jagmohan's dutiful wife and mother-in-law of Shaili, Priyanka and Abha. Pratibha loves her children & daughter-in-laws. She is badly traumatized due to the sudden demise of her husband.
Eldest son of Jagmohan and the husband of Shaili. He died in accident with Jagmohan Prakash and Veer.

Eldest daughter-in-law of Pratibha and wife of Vimal, she starts off hating Abha and she was very jealous of her and her husband Karan, she tries her best to get to their demise, but nevertheless she fails and learns her lesson for the good. After death of Vimal, she get remarried to Pankaj. She and Vimal have a daughhter Asmi.

Jagmohan and Pratibha's second son, he never claimed his rights as second eldest and he did not get far in life, eventually he got married to Priyanka, who influenced him for the worse, as soon as this happens his character turns sour and he becomes greedy and selfish, but later he understans the truth. He died in accident with Jagmohan, Vimal amd Prakash.

Second eldest daughter-in-law of Pratibha and wife of Veer, she turns out to be a prominent antagonist as she hates and is jealous of Abha. She also learns her lesson and get remarried after Veer's death.
Ranchod Jagmohan Prasaad / Siddharth Kumar / Ranchod Tiwari
Karan's twin brother, who was given away by Jagmohan at the time of his birth. He was to get married to Abha after Karan's fake death and loved her. He went away when Karan returned.

Head of the Thakur family. He owns the palatial citadel Swarn Bhawan. He believes in living a lavish lifestyle. He is proud of being a Thakur and has laid strict rules & regulations. But on the other hand, he is a family man and loves his family especially his children. He shows false pride. He learns lesson when he & his family are forced to leave Swarn Bhawan due to its auction.
Thakurain Chandra Prabha Uday Pratap Singh

Wife of Uday Pratap and mother of Prakash, Lata & Abha. She is an ideal wife & mother. She loves and cares for her husband & her children and worries for them. Unfortunately, she is murdered by Koyal.
Thakur Swarn Prakash Uday Pratap Singh / Prakash
Uday Pratap & Chandra Prabha's eldest son and husband of Kanika. He died in accident with Jagmohan, Vimal and Veer.

Daughter of Jagmohan and Prathibha, married to Swarn Prakash. Her character starts off as evil, she never missed a chance to insult Abha and her family but as the show prolonged she learns her lesson. After death of Prakash, she got remarried to Apoorva.
Chandra Prabha's foster brother, he allows the Thakur family to stay in his house with his wife Sheetal after they lost ownership of Swarn Bhavan.
She is the wife of Raghav. She hates the Thakur family and never misses a chance to insult them or throw them out of the house.
Karan's friend, Koyal's brother and Aruna's son, at first he loves and supports his sisters evil intentions, but after knowing the truth he disowned her. He later marries Lata and begins to love her.

She is eldest daughter of Thakur Uday Pratap and Chandra Prabha. She is a divorcee, who remarried to Raj Singhania, she begins to love him and she wishes to restore his family by giving her mother-in-law her rightful place
She is Raj's rightful and biological mother, she is driven away from her children by Daai Ma, but now her new daughter-in-law brings her back to claim her rights and her place in Raj's heart.
He wants to ruin Lata's life for the sake of his wife Koyal, who wants to hurt Abha

She hates Abha and tries her best to attack her and her family, she gets her husband to try to ruin Abha's sister Lata, she also killes Abha's mother Chandra Prabha to hurt Abha, but eventually her deeds caught up with her and she goes to jail therefore terminating her character
He is a learned doctor and he loves his wife Nilanjana, he ends up committing bad deeds in the name of his love, but later repents them
She is a good friend of Abha and is a dutiful wife and mother towards her husband and children, sadly she dies in a car accident therefore terminating her character
he is Yashodhara's son and he helps her in all her schemes, he is killed by his own wife in the end, therefore terminating his character
Wife of Dushyant and Daughter-in-law of Yashodhara, she also helps her in her schemes. She ends up killing her husband by mistake and is given the death sentence therefore terminating her character
Begins off liking Abha but he wrongs her al lot in the process of trying to marry her, in the end he learns his lesson and marries Sania
Karan's childhood friend that begins liking him, but marries and truly loves Sanskaar
He was the first husband of Swarn Lata. He used to torture and beat Lata for dowry after her family was forced to leave Swarn Bhawan. Divorced Lata, sent to jail for creating domestic violence
Yashodhara and Prathibha's evil brother, he supported Yashodhra in her evil plans and plots for the Prasaad family and Abha
She is a kind Doctor who treated Karan when he was near his death due to the severe car accident planned by Yashodhara. She started liking Karan.
She is a spiritual catalyst who can see the future and past. She helps Abha in discovering Karan who was lost in an accident. She also helps Abha's family to give 'Mukti' to Vasundhara's spirit.
Prosecution lawyer against Abha in Dushyant's murder case and Lata's fire breakout case
Troubled ghostly spirit lurking in the basements of Swarn Bhavan
Mother of Nilanjana & mother-in-law of Dr. Viren.
Father of Nilanjana and father-in-law of Viren
Abha's look-alike who wishes to take Abha's place in the Prasaad family and Karan's heart
She currently stays with Raj Singhania and his family. She is an antagonist, she hates Lata and Aruna, she wishes to drive them away from Raj so she can have him under her control

He is the brother of Nilanjana & son of Pramita. He left his parents, He enters Swarn Bhawan as a family charted accountant sent by Priyanka's parents to clear there her share of Swarn Bhawan. He is very evil and never misses a chance to turn Priyanka against her family. He also tries to marry Priyanka but is stopped by Abha. Later he get murdered by his boss Karuna.

Shaili's mother who entered Swarn Bhawan after the tragic death of men of Swarn Bhawan. She appears to be nice and helpful, but she actually arrives at Swarn Bhawan to name it for her daughter. She is the boss of Sushant and murders him.
She is an inspector who investigated the fire breakout of Lata and murder mystery of Sushant
